name: Udacity-cs253
tagline: My homework solutions for Udacity's Web Development course
body:
These are my class notes for Udacity's CS253. These are basically notes for myself so that I can remember the content in the class that is not captured in code. Anything to do with Google Apps Engine, or even plain HTML, will be in the code portion of this project.

The very basics of the web

Forms, and GET vs POST
